summary: AN ORDINANCE granting to the Northlake Plaza Limited Partnership permission to construct and maintain a auger cast piles and a grade beam in the North 34th Street - North 35th Street Alley, west of Albion Place North, to the rear of 936 North 34th Street for a ten year term, renewable for two successive ten year terms, specifying the conditions under which this permission is granted and providing for acceptance of the permit and conditions.
